import "./App.css"; import { CurriculoService } from "./services/CurriculoService"; import { CepService } from "./services/CepService"; import React from "react"; import InputMask from "react-input-mask" class App extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { uf: "", cidade: "", bairro: "", logradouro: "" } this.handleChange = this.handleChange.bind(this); this.buscarCep = this.buscarCep.bind(this); } Enviar = (e) => { console.log(e.target); CurriculoService.apiPost(e.target.data); }; async buscarCep() { const cep = document.querySelector(".cep").value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, ''); if (cep.lenght < 8) { return; } await CepService.ConsultaCep(cep).then((result) => { if (result.data.hasOwnProperty("erro")) { alert("CEP não existente"); } else { this.state.uf = result.data.uf; this.state.cidade = result.data.localidade; this.state.bairro = result.data.bairro; this.state.logradouro = result.data.logradouro; } }); } handleChange = (e) => { const value = e.target.value; const name = e.target.name; this.setState({ [name]: value }); }; render() { return (
